snippet.title: Card Sagas Wars - Master Chief VS Samus
snippet.description:
New preview video between Samus and Chief, who were completed several weeks ago. 
This match ended up really long because of usual AI stupidity and Crisis attacks, plus it's 3 rounds.  
We STILL can't update our site, and we didn't have time to bother with the blog idea yet either
but we are making a lot of progress! (no, really) 
This might be the last VS preview video, by the way

Music: Halo Theme Mjolnir Mix by Martin O'Donnell & Michael Salvatori

Time to goooo...
